{"tid":303908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為打入中國市場  美國化妝品公司NARS放棄原則 用動物作化妝品測試","createTime":"2017-06-30T13:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T04:28:40.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4172a1a36a3957d897085dd34e22064061e7bd79","tid":303908,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"NARS用動物作化妝品測試惹不滿<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】化妝品應否用動物作測試一直有很大爭論，為了保護動物權益，不少化妝產品都不再使用動物測試產品安全。<br />\n<br />\n英國《獨立報》報道，最近有一個外國化妝品品牌為了能夠進軍中國市場，放棄了自己本身的原則，同意用動物測試化妝品。<br />\n<br />\n美國化妝品公司NARS是不少網絡名人鍾愛的牌子，但近日他們就被批評為了能夠打入中國市場，毅然背棄了公司一直以來的原則，將化妝品用在動物身上作測試，因為中國強制規定在市面上出售的化妝品，都必需先經動物測試 。<br />\n<br />\n不少外國的網民都不滿NARS的做法，認為他們重視金錢多於自己的原則，更有網民發起抵制，罷買任何他們的產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=226723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226723&d=g5IBL8%2FQBGEtBEAJwJh3ifM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=b46da30b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226723&h=745c860e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=226723</a><br />\n<br />\nNARS就在社交網站回應，他們相信即使不經動物測試都能證明產品安全性，但他們必須遵從當地市場的法律要求。<br />\n<br />\n但有網民表示，此番說話只是再一次表達公司盈利大於動物的重要性。"},{"pid":"11b982b5e8d24c38f4c1493d3749036f5aa85dad","tid":303908,"uid":68285,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"因為俾狗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7e6ac9f59bc5f2a17f4b8959a5bd064c500224","tid":303908,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為俾狗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔喺動物身上用<br />\n啲大陸豬一陣有事咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9e44ec5a4987afdfcc1eb37c4bd79412f5ee89","tid":303908,"uid":150140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"可悲 可恥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}